	(11, 4, '2012-07-14 02:50:03', '2012-07-14 02:50:03', '<strong>Dormitories</strong>\r\n\r\nThe girls dormitoryaccommodates42 and the boys\' 34 in double decker bunks, with attached shower/toilet blocks. Shower/toilet facilities for special needs persons are provided in each dormitory.\r\n\r\n<strong>Guest rooms:</strong>\r\n\r\nTwo rooms are located at the end of the kitchen/dining room building. Each accommodates four persons and has its own ensuite.\r\n\r\n<strong>Recreation Area:</strong>\r\n\r\nFor outdoor games and sports. Bushwalks, table tennis and games equipments are available.\r\n\r\n<strong>Dining Hall:</strong>\r\n\r\nSeats 100 people with all crockery and cutlery provided. The kitchen is well equipped with gas stoves, diswasher, bain marie and cooking utensils. A PA system is located in the dining hall. An outdoor gas BBQ is situated near the dining hall.\r\n\r\n<strong>Assembly Hall:</strong>\r\n\r\nSeats 100 people. A piano, overhead projector, blackboard and whiteboard are provided in this room.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://koojare.won/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/Hall.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-169" alt="Hall" src="http://koojare.won/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/Hall-300x169.jpg" width="300" height="169" /></a>', 'Our Facilities', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'facilities', '', '', '2013-04-19 21:37:52', '2013-04-19 21:37:52', '', 0, 'http://localhost/koojarewon/?page_id=11', 0, 'page', '', 0),
