/wp-content/uploads/2009/03/family-portrait-tiops.jpg" alt="family-portrait-tiops.jpg" width="600" height="401" />\r\n<div>Read more: <a href="http://digital-photography-school.com/family-portraits-dos-and-donts#ixzz20hdMI6Cw">http://digital-photography-school.com/family-portraits-dos-and-donts#ixzz20hdMI6Cw</a></div>', 'Our Facilities', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '11-revision-7', '', '', '2012-07-18 06:11:12', '2012-07-18 06:11:12', '', 11, 'http://prowebtat.com/project_wordpress/koojarewon/?p=120', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
